[
  {
    "text": "So how do we learn?",
    "uid": "982c17c15f73e7c1",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 14.38,
    "end": 16.38
  },
  {
    "text": "And why do some of us learn things more easily than others?",
    "uid": "e5a92c526fc4d26d",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 16.38,
    "end": 20.38
  },
  {
    "text": "So as I was mentioned, I'm Dr. Larboid.",
    "uid": "901853ee52b6eb4d",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 21.38,
    "end": 24.38
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm a brain researcher here at the University of British Columbia.",
    "uid": "d187ff8751a4fbc4",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 24.38,
    "end": 27.38
  },
  {
    "text": "These are the questions that fascinate me.",
    "uid": "d891ea52140fb6d8",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 27.38,
    "end": 30.38
  },
  {
    "text": "So brain research is one of the great frontiers in the understanding of human physiology,",
    "uid": "b136ad93b0ba108b",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 30.38,
    "end": 40.48
  },
  {
    "text": "and also in the consideration of what makes us who we are.",
    "uid": "12009eba0be0d284",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 40.48,
    "end": 44.48
  },
  {
    "text": "It's an amazing time to be a brain researcher, and I would argue to you that I have the most interesting job in the world.",
    "uid": "d07b0c6de499d86a",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 45.48,
    "end": 51.48
  },
  {
    "text": "What we know about the brain is changing at a breathtaking pace.",
    "uid": "f2d3478fa910f68e",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 51.48,
    "end": 55.48
  },
  {
    "text": "And much of what we thought we knew and understood about the brain turns out to be not true or incomplete.",
    "uid": "55dbfe61c1989940",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 55.48,
    "end": 62.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Now some of these misconceptions are more obvious than others.",
    "uid": "4b48b12adc3a06fc",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 62.48,
    "end": 66.48
  },
  {
    "text": "For example, we used to think that after childhood, the brain did not really could not change,",
    "uid": "0964a60ac1d18bd1",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 66.48,
    "end": 73.48
  },
  {
    "text": "and it turns out that nothing could be farther from the truth.",
    "uid": "2268fa74b250995b",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 73.48,
    "end": 77.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Another misconception about the brain is that you only use parts of it at any given time and silent when you do nothing.",
    "uid": "9bb3fcecc06295db",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 77.48,
    "end": 84.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, this is also untrue.",
    "uid": "4ca2f8cc8f3d2ac6",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 84.48,
    "end": 86.48
  },
  {
    "text": "It turns out that even when you're at rest, thinking of nothing, your brain is highly active.",
    "uid": "ec5fd655bd1f45db",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 86.48,
    "end": 92.48
  },
  {
    "text": "So it's been advances in technology such as MRI.",
    "uid": "4bc81c6614395b84",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 92.48,
    "end": 96.48
  },
  {
    "text": "It's allowed us to make these and many other important discoveries.",
    "uid": "0edd211bdf99ed98",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 96.48,
    "end": 100.48
  },
  {
    "text": "And perhaps the most exciting, the most interesting and transformative these discoveries is that every time you learn a new factor, skill, you change your brain.",
    "uid": "2154346d55ceeac9",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 100.48,
    "end": 110.48
  },
  {
    "text": "It's something we call neuroplasticity.",
    "uid": "19ba76c5371dcb25",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 110.48,
    "end": 113.48
  },
  {
    "text": "So as little as 25 years ago, we thought that after about puberty, the only changes it took place in the brain were negative.",
    "uid": "6cca673c046a7215",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 113.48,
    "end": 120.48
  },
  {
    "text": "The loss of brain cells with aging, the result of damage, like a stroke.",
    "uid": "92caef66dc7c2aa8",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 120.48,
    "end": 125.48
  },
  {
    "text": "And then studies began to show remarkable amounts of reorganization in the adult brain.",
    "uid": "4192e981d79d5d3d",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 125.48,
    "end": 132.48
  },
  {
    "text": "And the assuming research has shown us that all of our behaviors change our brain.",
    "uid": "2c4043a149e46732",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 132.48,
    "end": 139.48
  },
  {
    "text": "That these changes are not limited by age.",
    "uid": "c08c5cf7e3784f27",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 139.48,
    "end": 142.48
  },
  {
    "text": "It's good news, right?",
    "uid": "708734f35e4eacd4",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 142.48,
    "end": 144.48
  },
  {
    "text": "And in fact, they're taking place all the time.",
    "uid": "a28784f654003e96",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 144.48,
    "end": 147.48
  },
  {
    "text": "And very importantly, brain organization helps to support recovery after you damage your brain.",
    "uid": "71d2fbb1f77c3942",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 147.48,
    "end": 153.48
  },
  {
    "text": "The key to each of these changes is neuroplasticity.",
    "uid": "8845f48f9d4efc39",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 153.48,
    "end": 158.48
  },
  {
    "text": "So what does it look like?",
    "uid": "4164787e6dc8e4ee",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 158.48,
    "end": 160.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Your brain can change in three very basic ways to support learning.",
    "uid": "b85ded70fb3030e9",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 160.48,
    "end": 165.48
  },
  {
    "text": "And the first is chemical.",
    "uid": "93fa937ac2c9a9ee",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 165.48,
    "end": 167.48
  },
  {
    "text": "To brain actually functions by transferring chemical signals between brain cells, what we call neurons,",
    "uid": "ed44f4a3934c1a9a",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 167.48,
    "end": 173.48
  },
  {
    "text": "and these trigger a series of actions and reactions.",
    "uid": "1a53d5a82d666158",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 173.48,
    "end": 176.48
  },
  {
    "text": "So to support learning, your brain can increase the amount of the concentrations of these chemical signaling,",
    "uid": "34ec38b0c7b2f84a",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 176.48,
    "end": 182.48
  },
  {
    "text": "that's taking place between neurons.",
    "uid": "2e0931620d0b5de5",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 182.48,
    "end": 185.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, because this kind of change can happen very rapidly, this supports short-term memory,",
    "uid": "f825164fae007898",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 185.48,
    "end": 190.48
  },
  {
    "text": "or the short-term improvement in the performance of a motor skill.",
    "uid": "c0cf44d4e5e8817f",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 190.48,
    "end": 194.48
  },
  {
    "text": "The second way that the brain can change to support learning is by altering its structure.",
    "uid": "d7a2735fc289dd3d",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 194.48,
    "end": 200.48
  },
  {
    "text": "So during learning, the brain can change the connections between neurons.",
    "uid": "cc475f40aee8f077",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 200.48,
    "end": 204.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, here are the physical structure of the brain is actually changing, so this takes a bit more time.",
    "uid": "ddb32b837feb5ed5",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 204.48,
    "end": 209.48
  },
  {
    "text": "These types of changes are related to long-term memory, long-term improvement in a motor skill.",
    "uid": "5db76add20a0b830",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 209.48,
    "end": 215.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, these processes that interact, and let me give you an example of how.",
    "uid": "0dba04991ddee162",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 215.48,
    "end": 220.48
  },
  {
    "text": "So we've all tried to learn a new motor skill, maybe playing the piano, maybe learning to juggle.",
    "uid": "6e9878e92510c282",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 220.48,
    "end": 227.48
  },
  {
    "text": "And you've had the experience of getting better and better within a single session of practice, and thinking, I've got it.",
    "uid": "858b99c2c15ad9b0",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 227.48,
    "end": 234.48
  },
  {
    "text": "And then, maybe you've returned the next day and all those improvements from the day before they're lost.",
    "uid": "fb9d4428d839cf79",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 234.48,
    "end": 240.48
  },
  {
    "text": "What happened? Well, in the short-term, your brain was able to increase the chemical signaling between your neurons.",
    "uid": "f3dab5f430a02a03",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 240.48,
    "end": 247.48
  },
  {
    "text": "But for some reason, those changes did not induce the structural change that are necessary to support long-term memory.",
    "uid": "b41eda8b46b3c6ef",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 247.48,
    "end": 256.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Remember that long-term memories take time, and what you see in the short-term does not reflect learning.",
    "uid": "c215e040abef6e82",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 256.48,
    "end": 262.48
  },
  {
    "text": "It's these physical changes that are now going to support long-term memories and chemical changes that support short-term memories.",
    "uid": "67fc51a008bf597d",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 262.48,
    "end": 271.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Structural changes also can lead to integrated networks of brain regions that function together to support learning,",
    "uid": "0cb29ca05044e45f",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 271.48,
    "end": 278.48
  },
  {
    "text": "and they can also lead to certain brain regions that are important for very specific behaviors to change the structure or to enlarge.",
    "uid": "aa910e8f8878e7a7",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 278.48,
    "end": 285.48
  },
  {
    "text": "So, here are some examples of that.",
    "uid": "4d906197f841b48c",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 285.48,
    "end": 288.48
  },
  {
    "text": "So, people who read Braille, they have larger hand-sensory areas in their brain than those of us who don't.",
    "uid": "3371001a74e912d5",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 288.48,
    "end": 295.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Your dominant hand motor region, which is on the left side of your brain, if your right-handed, is larger than the other side.",
    "uid": "14a80a6cc27420bc",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 295.48,
    "end": 303.48
  },
  {
    "text": "And research shows that London taxi cab drivers who actually have to memorize a map of London to get their taxi cab license,",
    "uid": "1553aaf9c83ddb8f",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 303.48,
    "end": 311.48
  },
  {
    "text": "they have larger brain regions devoted to spatial or mapping memories.",
    "uid": "869fa9b1a0b6f7d9",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 311.48,
    "end": 316.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, the last way that your brain can change to support learning is by altering its function.",
    "uid": "831f2872d301145b",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 316.48,
    "end": 322.48
  },
  {
    "text": "As you use a brain region, it becomes more and more excitable and easy to use again.",
    "uid": "1998abd6818fffb3",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 322.48,
    "end": 328.48
  },
  {
    "text": "And as your brain has these areas, it increase their excitability, the brain shifts how and when they're activated.",
    "uid": "5b9682bb4229fc17",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 328.48,
    "end": 335.48
  },
  {
    "text": "With learning, we see that whole networks of brain activity are shifting and changing.",
    "uid": "379348d73e20ed2a",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 335.48,
    "end": 341.48
  },
  {
    "text": "So, neuroplasticity is supported by chemical, by structural, and by functional changes.",
    "uid": "731f2dd9ff1910db",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 341.48,
    "end": 348.48
  },
  {
    "text": "And these are happening across the whole brain.",
    "uid": "2c3543614e31615e",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 348.48,
    "end": 351.48
  },
  {
    "text": "They can occur in isolation from one another, but most often they take place in concert.",
    "uid": "ac549a4e44c253c2",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 351.48,
    "end": 356.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Together, they support learning, and they're taking place all the time.",
    "uid": "ba959f9b3501fb62",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 356.48,
    "end": 363.86
  },
  {
    "text": "So, just told you really how awesomely neuroplastic your brain is.",
    "uid": "c5e183366795f8e3",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 363.86,
    "end": 368.86
  },
  {
    "text": "So, why can't you learn anything you choose to with ease?",
    "uid": "d5c69a4fa5f29cc0",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 368.86,
    "end": 372.86
  },
  {
    "text": "Why do our kids sometimes fail in school?",
    "uid": "4bae0208bff9ea43",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 372.86,
    "end": 376.86
  },
  {
    "text": "Why do we age to pretend to forget things?",
    "uid": "109e95f4f0cb5499",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 376.86,
    "end": 379.86
  },
  {
    "text": "And why don't people fully recover from brain damage?",
    "uid": "f414ac8c688fbce6",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 379.86,
    "end": 383.86
  },
  {
    "text": "That is, what is it that limits and facilitates neuroplasticity?",
    "uid": "da7bcc11b19dcaca",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 383.86,
    "end": 388.86
  },
  {
    "text": "And so, this is what I study.",
    "uid": "c0173a8b2dedf8b2",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 388.86,
    "end": 390.86
  },
  {
    "text": "I study it specifically how it relates to recovery from stroke.",
    "uid": "6275e8b365ab5040",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 390.86,
    "end": 394.86
  },
  {
    "text": "So, recently, stroke dropped from being the third leading cause of death in the United States to be the fourth leading cause of death.",
    "uid": "4ef453d035c2bd4f",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 394.86,
    "end": 401.86
  },
  {
    "text": "Great news, right?",
    "uid": "370068036e7b1f42",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 401.86,
    "end": 403.86
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, it actually turns out that the numbers of people having a stroke has not declined.",
    "uid": "7b9438bf135c2f46",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 403.86,
    "end": 408.86
  },
  {
    "text": "We're just better at keeping people alive after a severe stroke.",
    "uid": "d91be789041c4da1",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 408.86,
    "end": 412.86
  },
  {
    "text": "It turns out to be very difficult to help the brain recover from stroke.",
    "uid": "2d64e6cf1dee1671",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 412.86,
    "end": 417.86
  },
  {
    "text": "And frankly, we have failed to develop effective rehabilitation interventions.",
    "uid": "efe6614bc1772c8b",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 417.86,
    "end": 422.86
  },
  {
    "text": "The net result of this is that stroke is the leading cause of long-term disability in adults in the world.",
    "uid": "0ea80b3cede3f6c0",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 422.86,
    "end": 432.62
  },
  {
    "text": "Individuals with stroke are younger and tending to live longer with that disability.",
    "uid": "05134a5d2af99a79",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 432.62,
    "end": 438.62
  },
  {
    "text": "And research from microbactually shows that the health related quality of life of Canadians with stroke has declined.",
    "uid": "e0d9a4a07801fd5a",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 438.62,
    "end": 445.62
  },
  {
    "text": "So, clearly, we need to be better at helping people recover from stroke.",
    "uid": "c103ceb559230fa2",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 445.62,
    "end": 449.62
  },
  {
    "text": "And this is an enormous societal problem and it's one that we're not solving.",
    "uid": "e0f4331b80a41552",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 449.62,
    "end": 455.62
  },
  {
    "text": "So, what can be done?",
    "uid": "5b49e450d201bcaf",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 455.62,
    "end": 458.62
  },
  {
    "text": "One thing is absolutely clear.",
    "uid": "f54573f4528c3520",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 458.62,
    "end": 460.62
  },
  {
    "text": "The best driver of neuroplastic change in your brain is your behavior.",
    "uid": "ad6efbbbc078b4d2",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 460.62,
    "end": 465.62
  },
  {
    "text": "The problem is that the dose of behavior, the dose of practice that's required to learn new and relearn old motor skills,",
    "uid": "5a20931657ec4d5d",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 465.62,
    "end": 473.62
  },
  {
    "text": "it's very large.",
    "uid": "5358420b932cfda8",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 473.62,
    "end": 475.62
  },
  {
    "text": "And how do we effectively deliver these large doses of practice?",
    "uid": "e5ed30528225f7dd",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 475.62,
    "end": 478.62
  },
  {
    "text": "Is a very difficult problem.",
    "uid": "8f8ce009c79f23df",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 478.62,
    "end": 480.62
  },
  {
    "text": "It's also a very expensive problem.",
    "uid": "342378004c2a263a",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 480.62,
    "end": 482.62
  },
  {
    "text": "So, the approach that my research has taken is to develop therapies that prime or that prepare the brain to learn.",
    "uid": "a529e83ae21c24e3",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 482.62,
    "end": 488.62
  },
  {
    "text": "And these have included brain stimulation, exercise, and robotics.",
    "uid": "7d2f1223174f9c2d",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 488.62,
    "end": 493.62
  },
  {
    "text": "But through my research, I've realized that a major limitation to the development of therapies that speed recovery from stroke",
    "uid": "1db6f754acf1169b",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 493.62,
    "end": 501.62
  },
  {
    "text": "is that patterns of neuroplasticity are highly variable from person to person.",
    "uid": "93fb5bd60f1ce9ae",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 501.62,
    "end": 508.62
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, as a researcher, variability used to drive me crazy.",
    "uid": "48ca1c501a81c85d",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 508.62,
    "end": 512.62
  },
  {
    "text": "It makes it very difficult to use statistics to test your data and your ideas.",
    "uid": "2c2dbc065e56c7d1",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 512.62,
    "end": 518.62
  },
  {
    "text": "And because of this, medical interventions that are specifically designed to minimize variability.",
    "uid": "40a8b6719a079006",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 518.62,
    "end": 524.62
  },
  {
    "text": "But in my research, it's becoming really clear that the most important, the most informative data that we collect,",
    "uid": "1a5d6c65d7879ddf",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 524.62,
    "end": 531.62
  },
  {
    "text": "is showing this variability.",
    "uid": "7c46f23a5adbe4b4",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 531.62,
    "end": 534.62
  },
  {
    "text": "So, by studying the brain after stroke, we've learned a lot.",
    "uid": "7bae97fa21ae1575",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 534.62,
    "end": 540.93
  },
  {
    "text": "And I think these lessons are very valuable in other areas.",
    "uid": "90f0afdd56bb5e90",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 540.93,
    "end": 545.93
  },
  {
    "text": "So, the first lesson is that the primary driver of change in your brain is your behavior.",
    "uid": "94816748209a2c66",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 545.93,
    "end": 551.93
  },
  {
    "text": "So, there's no neuroplasticity drug you can take.",
    "uid": "84deb5a12e7b2b99",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 551.93,
    "end": 555.93
  },
  {
    "text": "Nothing is more effective than practice at helping you learn.",
    "uid": "8e16c3a12ab7e075",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 555.93,
    "end": 558.93
  },
  {
    "text": "And the bottom line is you have to do the work.",
    "uid": "f538c77ca9d7bd5a",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 558.93,
    "end": 563.93
  },
  {
    "text": "In fact, my research has shown that increased difficulty, increased struggle if you will during practice,",
    "uid": "116969a1236f3e73",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 563.93,
    "end": 569.93
  },
  {
    "text": "asia leads to both more learning and greater structural change in the brain.",
    "uid": "092e6211cdb30239",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 569.93,
    "end": 575.93
  },
  {
    "text": "The problem here is that neuroplasticity can work both ways.",
    "uid": "7ca533c5b517af37",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 575.93,
    "end": 582.46
  },
  {
    "text": "It can be positive, you learn something new, and you refine the motor skill.",
    "uid": "b1b11e58b336e7f9",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 582.46,
    "end": 587.46
  },
  {
    "text": "It can be negative though.",
    "uid": "4eed4a9b300eb612",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 587.46,
    "end": 589.46
  },
  {
    "text": "You forgot something you want new.",
    "uid": "9132ccfc0d701908",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 589.46,
    "end": 591.46
  },
  {
    "text": "You've become addicted to drugs.",
    "uid": "8b87441fc7f6d743",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 591.46,
    "end": 593.46
  },
  {
    "text": "Maybe you have chronic pain.",
    "uid": "c9ec6274af458b3d",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 593.46,
    "end": 595.46
  },
  {
    "text": "So, your brain is tremendously plastic, and it's being shaped both structurally and functionally, but everything you do.",
    "uid": "2647867c1dc4f1ff",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 595.46,
    "end": 602.46
  },
  {
    "text": "But also, by everything that you don't do.",
    "uid": "dc33966b079ee7d2",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 602.46,
    "end": 606.46
  },
  {
    "text": "The second lesson we've learned about the brain is that there is no one-size-fits-all approach to learning.",
    "uid": "e15c47edce6be516",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 606.46,
    "end": 613.46
  },
  {
    "text": "So, there's no recipe for learning.",
    "uid": "15f157e60986a585",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 613.46,
    "end": 616.46
  },
  {
    "text": "Consider the popular belief that it takes 10,000 hours of practice to learn and to master a new motor skill.",
    "uid": "049bb81c76e816bc",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 616.46,
    "end": 623.46
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, I can assure you, it is not quite that simple.",
    "uid": "d62d05f8ac464452",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 623.46,
    "end": 626.46
  },
  {
    "text": "For some of us, it's going to take a lot more practice, and for others it may take far less.",
    "uid": "8c8ca85193832f64",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 626.46,
    "end": 632.46
  },
  {
    "text": "So, the shaping of our plastic brains is far too unique for there to be any single intervention that's going to work for all of us.",
    "uid": "5f5117513f1a77a9",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 632.46,
    "end": 640.46
  },
  {
    "text": "And now, this realization has forced us to consider something called personalized medicine.",
    "uid": "3fab8a5fb00bed43",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 640.46,
    "end": 645.46
  },
  {
    "text": "So, this is the idea that to optimize outcomes each individual requires their own intervention.",
    "uid": "1d757d89b8107161",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 645.46,
    "end": 652.46
  },
  {
    "text": "And the idea actually comes from cancer treatments.",
    "uid": "ce8e1dfacc0dcaa6",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 652.46,
    "end": 655.46
  },
  {
    "text": "And here it turns out that genetics are very important in matching certain types of chemotherapy with specific forms of cancer.",
    "uid": "dde3c45f6e2c9fa0",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 655.46,
    "end": 663.46
  },
  {
    "text": "My research is showing that this also applies to recovery from stroke.",
    "uid": "b335526acdf8f7e7",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 663.46,
    "end": 667.46
  },
  {
    "text": "So, there are certain characteristics of brain structure and function that we call biomarkers.",
    "uid": "e060e8d21d669626",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 667.46,
    "end": 672.46
  },
  {
    "text": "And these biomarkers are proving to be very helpful in helping us to match specific therapies with individual patients.",
    "uid": "9391fd22f5ca11cd",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 672.46,
    "end": 680.46
  },
  {
    "text": "And the data from my lab suggests it's a combination of biomarkers that best predicts neuroplastic change and patterns of recovery after stroke.",
    "uid": "d914f9da77c941f1",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 680.46,
    "end": 688.46
  },
  {
    "text": "And that's not surprising given how complicated the human brain is.",
    "uid": "028e2df973b58c01",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 688.46,
    "end": 693.46
  },
  {
    "text": "But I also think we can consider this concept much more broadly.",
    "uid": "823d83be314aa3eb",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 693.46,
    "end": 698.46
  },
  {
    "text": "Given the unique structure and function of each of our brains, what we've learned about neuroplasticity after stroke applies to everyone.",
    "uid": "8dffe06c5a8013bf",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 698.46,
    "end": 708.46
  },
  {
    "text": "The haters that you employ in your everyday life are important.",
    "uid": "84b813e7fdd0721b",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 708.46,
    "end": 714.81
  },
  {
    "text": "Each of them is changing your brain.",
    "uid": "c3607560e8832687",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 714.81,
    "end": 716.81
  },
  {
    "text": "And I believe we have to consider not just personalized medicine, but personalized learning.",
    "uid": "1a808b0b7182b007",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 716.81,
    "end": 722.81
  },
  {
    "text": "The uniqueness of your brain will affect you both as a learner and also as a teacher.",
    "uid": "af56485274d9edee",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 722.81,
    "end": 728.81
  },
  {
    "text": "And now this idea helps us to understand why some children can thrive in traditional education settings and others don't.",
    "uid": "2e28c7d23f238ac4",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 728.81,
    "end": 736.81
  },
  {
    "text": "Or some of us can learn languages easily, and yet others can pick up any sport and excel.",
    "uid": "0d42a380d5c8eff6",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 736.81,
    "end": 742.81
  },
  {
    "text": "So when you leave this room today, your brain will not be the same as when you entered this morning.",
    "uid": "213a9454adfec545",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 742.81,
    "end": 752.25
  },
  {
    "text": "And I think that's pretty amazing.",
    "uid": "a8eb2d2ada76a630",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 752.25,
    "end": 755.25
  },
  {
    "text": "But each of you is going to have change your brain differently.",
    "uid": "042a3c32e925f000",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 755.25,
    "end": 760.25
  },
  {
    "text": "Understanding these differences, these individual patterns, this variability and change, is going to enable the next graded events in neuroscience.",
    "uid": "4a1354f0be4dd749",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 760.25,
    "end": 769.25
  },
  {
    "text": "It's going to allow us to develop new and more effective interventions, and allow for matches between learners and teachers and patients and interventions.",
    "uid": "b4d4f31501db9225",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 769.25,
    "end": 780.25
  },
  {
    "text": "And this does not just apply to recovery from stroke.",
    "uid": "2d8d3c0d230bfb64",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 780.25,
    "end": 783.25
  },
  {
    "text": "It applies to each of us as a parent, as a teacher, as a manager, and also because you're at TEDx today, a lifelong learner.",
    "uid": "48a4528ff5ff2ed8",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 783.25,
    "end": 792.25
  },
  {
    "text": "Study how and what you learn best.",
    "uid": "e0bdff4cd587c73c",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 792.25,
    "end": 796.25
  },
  {
    "text": "Repeat those behaviors that are healthy for your brain and break those behaviors and habits that are not practice.",
    "uid": "151f151e83130fff",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 796.25,
    "end": 805.25
  },
  {
    "text": "Learning is about doing the work that your brain requires.",
    "uid": "92355cce1d8b30f5",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 805.25,
    "end": 810.25
  },
  {
    "text": "So the best strategies are going to vary between individuals.",
    "uid": "c2c478910b16da3c",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 810.25,
    "end": 814.25
  },
  {
    "text": "You know what? They're even going to vary within individuals.",
    "uid": "dbab645f7c8f5910",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 814.25,
    "end": 817.25
  },
  {
    "text": "So for you learning music may come very easily, but learning to snowboard much harder.",
    "uid": "2f1bc618a7668ff3",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 817.25,
    "end": 823.25
  },
  {
    "text": "I hope that you leave today with a new appreciation of how magnificent your brain is.",
    "uid": "7249e346b69bec21",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 823.25,
    "end": 829.25
  },
  {
    "text": "You and your plastic brain are constantly being shaped by the world around you.",
    "uid": "d9017aa46d6d322f",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 829.25,
    "end": 834.25
  },
  {
    "text": "Understand that everything you do, everything you encounter, and everything you experience is changing your brain, and that can be for better, but it can also be for worse.",
    "uid": "0a253c3c94db6e04",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 834.25,
    "end": 845.25
  },
  {
    "text": "So when you leave today, go out and build the brain you want.",
    "uid": "90ca79f1f83b799c",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 845.25,
    "end": 850.25
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you very much.",
    "uid": "55bfd6cfbb2bb567",
    "source": "TEDx_Talks - After_watching_this_your_brain_will_not_be_the_same_Lara_Boyd_TEDxV",
    "start": 850.25,
    "end": 852.25
  }
]